1.	AIM: 
To design and develop a Full E-Commerce Website using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript that allows users to view products, navigate between pages, and interact with a simple online shopping interface. 
 
 
2.	OBJECTIVES: 
•	To create a multi-page website using HTML. 
•	To design an attractive user interface using CSS. 
•	To implement interactivity using JavaScript. 
•	To display products with images and prices. 
•	To provide navigation between Home, About, Service, and Contact pages. 
•	To understand the structure of an e-commerce website. 
 
3.	ALGORITHM: 
Step 1: Start the program 
Step 2: Display the Home page 
Step 3: Show navigation menu 
Step 4: Display product list with images 
Step 5: Allow user to navigate to other pages 
Step 6: Accept user input in contact form 
Step 7: Display submitted information Step 8: Stop the program 
 
4.	FUTURE ENHANCEMENT: 
•	Add login and registration system 
•	Connect to database 
•	Add payment gateway 
•	Add search functionality 
•	Improve security 
 
 
